<br>
I think when they're talking about slows (usually in reference to damage output by a melee) the % has to do with the relative amount of damage output compared to a nonslow.<br>
<br>
So a 50% slow would mean you're putting out half the damage you normally would.<br>
<br>
If you apply this to heals, at 50% slowed, you'd put out half the healing you normally would, which would lead to 2x casting times.<br>
<br>
I'm sure we can test this out if you want <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
